                                "text": "jeroenooms@gmail.com"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "\n\nWe found that the r-base debian package fails to build on Ubuntu 26.04 (even\nthough it succeeds to build manually). The bug is caused by a "
                            },
