                                "type": "text",
                                "text": " command in\nsrc\/unix\/Makefile.in which uses a colon as the delimiter. \n\nRecent Linux distros add "
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "--package-metadata=...",
                                "style": {
                                    "code": true
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": " to the LDFLAGS, and the value\nfor this flag contains colons. So the minimal fix is to use another delimiter\nin sed, e.g: "
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "link",
                                "url": "https:\/\/github.com\/r-devel\/r-svn\/pull\/253.diff"
